<P>A SERMON, <HI>OCCASIONED BY THE</HI> DEATH OF GEN. GEORGE WASHINGTON, <HI>LATE PRESIDENT OF THE UNITED STATES OF AMERICA:</HI> DELIVERED <HI>AT LEBANON, IN THE TOWN OF CANAAN, FEBRUARY</HI> 22<HI>d,</HI> 1800.</P>
<P>BY SILAS CHURCHILL, A. M. PASTOR OF THE FIRST PRESBYTERIAN CHURCH IN CANAAN.</P>
<P>ALBANY: <HI>PRINTED BY BARBER AND SOUTHWICK,</HI> FAUST's <HI>Statue,</HI> State-Street. <ABBR>M,DCCC.</ABBR></P>
