<P><HI>Re&s;olved unanimou&s;ly,</HI> That Brother <HI>Eli|&s;ha Gilbert,</HI> Brother <HI>John Butler,</HI> and Bro|ther <HI>Jo&s;iah Patter&s;on</HI> be, and they are hereby appointed a committee to return the thanks of this Lodge to the Rev. Brother SILAS CHURCHILL, for the Sermon deliver|ed before &s;aid Lodge, and a very crouded audience of the citizens of this and the ad|jacent towns, on the 22d day of February la&s;t at Lebanon; and reque&s;t a copy there|of to be printed.</P>
